                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Bayard</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Gresham</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">London</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1894-03-29">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 29, 1894</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Had an interview with, minister for foreign affairs. Your instructions by cable
                    communicated. Will reply as soon as possible.</p>
            </div>
